  <h2 class="h2link">All Ideas Have Ancestors</h2>
  

<div class="date">
	Posted: <span>September 19th 2012.</span>
Tags:
	
		<span>
			<a href="/tag/ideas">Ideas</a>
			, 
		</span>
	
		<span>
			<a href="/tag/video">Video</a>
			
		</span>
	
